## 7) Training and evaluation interaction (sequence diagram)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Notebook
    participant DataLoader
    participant Baseline as Baseline CNN
    participant GACNN as GA-CNN
    participant Metrics
    participant Results as JSON Results

    User->>Notebook: Run experiment cells
    Notebook->>DataLoader: Load batches (images, labels)

    loop For each epoch
        Notebook->>Baseline: Train on batch
        Baseline-->>Notebook: Predictions + loss
        Notebook->>GACNN: Train on batch
        GACNN-->>Notebook: Predictions + loss
    end

    Notebook->>Baseline: Evaluate on test set
    Baseline-->>Metrics: Predictions
    Notebook->>GACNN: Evaluate on test set
    GACNN-->>Metrics: Predictions

    Notebook->>Metrics: Run robustness tests
    Metrics-->>Notebook: Accuracy/F1/AUC/robustness summaries
    Notebook->>Results: Save summary and detailed JSON files
    Results-->>User: Final comparison outputs
```

---

## 8) Robustness testing flow (sequence diagram)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Evaluator
    participant Transform as Image Transform
    participant Model
    participant Score as Accuracy Score

    Evaluator->>Transform: Apply rotation / blur / noise / brightness
    Transform-->>Evaluator: Modified test images
    Evaluator->>Model: Predict on modified images
    Model-->>Evaluator: Predicted labels
    Evaluator->>Score: Compare predicted vs true labels
    Score-->>Evaluator: Robustness metric per condition
```

